The paper discusses the design and performance analysis of pulse shaped OFDM for 5G systems, which is a topic related to communication systems and networking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely categories include cs.COMM (Communications), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
